          "answer": "played",
          "explanation": "一般过去时用动词过去式"
        },
        {
          "question": "He _____ the car.",
          "answer": "stopped",
          "explanation": "重读闭音节双写辅音加-ed"
        }
      ]
    },
    "transformation": {
